name: Ariel Winter LoRA
description:
A Stable Diffusion LoRA profile based on Ariel Winter.

Dunno wtf happened here, not a single NSFW image of her was used, but this LoRA is creating more NSFW images than any of my other profiles. Also, hate that I need to say this, but no images were used of her below the age of 18.

Place it in "stable-diffusion-webui\extensions\sd-webui-additional-networks\models\lora" folder in Automatic1111 WebUI root folder.

Made using kohya-ss.

In txt2img, under "Additional Networks", select "Enable" and under Model 1 select "Ariel Winter" and assign a weight between 0.3-0.7 (I found 0.55 to be the sweet spot, but the weight required can change depending on the checkpoint being used - feel free to experiment!). In the prompt text window use "Ariel Winter" within your prompt to generate images.

Embed has been trained on Stable Diffusion 1.5 model.
